Publisher Stories

1 As a publisher, I can upload my paper and monitor the reviews my paper receives
2 A publisher is not able to change he’s account permission
3 Publisher can comment on the discussions related to he’s published paper

Reviewer Stories

1 A reviewer can review papers he’s been assigned to
2 As a reviewer, I  can put up a request to review a paper i haven't been assigned to yet


Chairman Stories    

1 As a chairman I can assign different reviewers to different papers based on their expertise 
2 I can view all the papers and the reviewers
3 I can monitor the flagging system and contact the admin about any system changes required

Admin Stories   

1 I can delete accounts based on the chairman suggestions
2 I can change accounts ranking system
3 I can monitor the entire application
